title: Bright West Facing One Bedroom! Floor to Ceiling Windows!
posting_body: ['Welcome to The Modern', 'Welcome to The Modern where first impressions are everything.', 'From the gracious greeting, you will receive upon arrival to the natural materials and finishes that act as an extension of the surrounding beauty, every detail has been carefully curated.', 'Beginning on the 13th floor, every one of our residences has a breathtaking panoramic view of Elliott Bay or the Seattle skyline with striking floor-to-ceiling windows.', 'The Conservatory is the heart of the building.', 'An exclusive club hall for a vertical neighborhood made up of six unique spaces that enliven two floors of the building: The Foyer, The Bar, The Video Wall, The Club Room, The Loft, and multiple private dining / executive board rooms.', 'The immediate area is rich with dozens of cultural attractions, restaurants, and nightlife options within walking distance, placing The Modern at the front steps of recreation.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Children’s Studio with day care available', 'Laundry and dry-cleaning services', '24-hour front desk coverage', 'Car washing and in-house luxury car share', 'Restaurant reservations and recommendations', 'After-hours snack menu', 'Paddleboard and bike rentals', 'In-home personal bartender', 'View dome butler service', 'Package service and in-home delivery', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
